			j B       ) next entry                           	?      ) show help
			k A       ) previous entry                       	5 6    ) page down/up
			h D       ) parent directory                     	⇈s \t  ) new tab, nexttab
			l C ''    ) cd or open file                      	> <    ) extra pane
			g G ⇑g    ) first/last entry, cd                 	_ | ¦  ) extra pane
			a         ) kill sound preview                   	-      ) next pane or viewer
			b ⇑b ⇈b   ) fzf find/all/dirs                    	/      ) find
			c ⇑c      ) copy to, show command mapping        	⇈i     ) fzfi, using ueberzurg
			d ⇑d ⇈d   ) delete, clear filters/history        	{      ) fzf to file with preview
			e E       ) external viewer, detached            	}      ) rg to file
			f F ⇑f ⇈f ) filter1/2, external, reverse         	:      ) go to entry
			H ⇑h ¨ ⇈h ) fzf history, global, global, edit    	:      ) command: q, etags, load_tags
			i I ⇑i    ) new file/directory, bulk             	' '    ) leader key
			J K       ) scroll preview
			⇑k        ) clear persistent marks               	, ;    ) persistent mark add/fzf
			L         ) symlink selection
			⇈l ⇑l     ) lock/unlock entry preview
			m         ) mark directory and file              	' ⇑'   ) go, fzf to mark
			M ⇑m ⇈m   ) view mode, montage/refresh           	)      ) file/dir view mode
			n N       ) find next/previous                   	=      ) preview directory only
			o O       ) sort type, reverse
			⇑o ⇈O     ) merge tags, fzf
			p P       ) copy/move selection
			r R       ) refresh, rename/bulk rename          	$      ) detach editor preview
			s S       ) shell pane, zoomed                   	!      ) run shell command
			⇑s        ) show/hide size                       	¡      ) pdh pane
			t T ⇑t    ) fzf tag, +subdir, to clipboard       	*      ) maximum listing depth
			⇈t        ) file preview at end                  	. ⇑.   ) show/hide dot-files/etags
			U u ⇑u    ) untag all, fzf, goto                 	^      ) show/hide stat
			v V       ) preview hide, once                   	#      ) show/hide extension preview
			⇑v ⇈v     ) ext. preview mode (media, pdf, tar)  	"      ) show/hide image preview
			w W       ) local mplayer, extra viewers         	+      ) change preview size
			x X       ) chmod a+x, a-x                       	% &    ) hide extension, enable all
			y Y ⇑y ⇈y ) tag/untag, files, all                	1-4    ) class tag
			q Q ⇑q ⇈q ) quit, forced, keep shell/ zoom       	0, 7-9 ) refresh, internal usage

			˽c        ) compress/decompress                  	˽x        ) PGP encrypt/decrypt
			˽s        ) stat file                            	˽z        ) password encrypt/decrypt
			˽m        ) mail
